uses In Berlin Amid Coronavirus Climate|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|date=March 16, 2020|access-date=March 16, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316180056/https://deadline.com/2020/03/the-matrix-4-coronavirus-production-stop-1202884580/|archive-date=March 16, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Midnight in the Switchgrass]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/midnight-in-the-switchgrass-postpone-coronavirus-puerto-rico-shoot-megan-fox-emile-hirsch-bruce-willis-machine-gun-kelly-randall-emmett-1202884454/|title=Indie 'Midnight In The Switchgrass' Postpones Puerto Rico Shoot Over Coronavirus Scare|first1=Mike Fleming|last1=Jr|first2=Mike Fleming|last2=Jr|date=March 16, 2020|access-date=March 16, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317051931/https://deadline.com/2020/03/midnight-in-the-switchgrass-postpone-coronavirus-puerto-rico-shoot-megan-fox-emile-hirsch-bruce-willis-machine-gun-kelly-randall-emmett-1202884454/|archive-date=March 17, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Mission: Impossible 7]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/mission-impossible-7-venice-italy-production-to-halt-due-to-coronavirus-1202867109/|title='Mission: Impossible 7' Venice, Italy Shoot To Halt Due To Coronavirus; Paramount Cites Abundance Of Caution \u2013 Update|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|date=February 24, 2020|access-date=March 14, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224215341/https://deadline.com/2020/02/mission-impossible-7-venice-italy-production-to-halt-due-to-coronavirus-1202867109/|archive-date=February 24, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Nightmare Alley (upcoming film)|Nightmare Alley]]''<ref name=\"HollywoodReporter\" />\n*''[[The Northman]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/news/coronavirus-fears-halt-line-of-duty-filming-in-northern-ireland-39047480.html|title=Coronavirus fears halt Line of Duty filming in Northern Ireland|website=[[Belfast Telegraph]]|date=March 16, 2020|accessdate=March 16, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317162251/https://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/news/coronavirus-fears-halt-line-of-duty-filming-in-northern-ireland-39047480.html|archive-date=March 17, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Official Competition]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/penelope-cruz-antonio-banderas-official-competition-suspends-spain-shoot-coronavirus-1202882152/|title=Spain's Mediapro Suspends Shoot On Pen\u00e9lope Cruz, Antonio Banderas Movie 'Official Competition' & Two Series Over Coronavirus|first1=Tom|last1=Grater|first2=Tom|last2=Grater|date=March 13, 2020|access-date=March 15, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200314135541/https://deadline.com/2020/03/penelope-cruz-antonio-banderas-official-competition-suspends-spain-shoot-coronavirus-1202882152/|archive-date=March 14, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[The Power of the Dog (film)|The Power of the Dog]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.if.com.au/see-saw-films-emile-sherman-ponders-the-post-pandemic-future/|title=See-Saw Films\u2019 Emile Sherman ponders the post-pandemic future|website=[[IF Magazine]]|first=Don|last=Groves|date=April 2, 2020|accessdate=April 10, 2020}}</ref>\n*''[[The Prom (film)|The Prom]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/coronavirus-ryan-murphy-postponed-nicole-kidman-meryl-streep-the-prom-netflix-paramount-1202880967/|title=Ryan Murphy's 'The Prom' Film Shuts Down Production Over Coronavirus Concerns|first1=Dominic|last1=Patten|first2=Dominic|last2=Patten|date=March 12, 2020|access-date=March 18, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318193507/https://deadline.com/2020/03/coronavirus-ryan-murphy-postponed-nicole-kidman-meryl-streep-the-prom-netflix-paramount-1202880967/|archive-date=March 18, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Red Notice (film)|Red Notice]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/studios-suspend-film-productions-coronavirus-concerns-1284602|title=Studios Suspend Film Productions Amid Coronavirus Concerns|website=The Hollywood Reporter}}</ref>\n*''[[Samaritan (2020 film)|Samaritan]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/sylvester-stallone-movie-the-samaritan-coronavirus-hiatus-1202883810/|title=Sylvester Stallone Superhero Thriller 'Samaritan' Going On Two-Week Hiatus|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|date=March 15, 2020|access-date=March 15, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316000107/https://deadline.com/2020/03/sylvester-stallone-movie-the-samaritan-coronavirus-hiatus-1202883810/|archive-date=March 16, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings]]''<ref name=\"HollywoodReporter\" />\n*''[[The Tragedy of Macbeth (upcoming film)|The Tragedy of Macbeth]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/denzel-washington-macbeth-movie-hiatus-coronavirus-1202893688/|title=Denzel Washington, Frances McDormand, Joel Coen A24 'Macbeth' Movie On Hiatus|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|last2=D'Alessandro|date=March 26, 2020|accessdate=April 7, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401201427/https://deadline.com/2020/03/denzel-washington-macbeth-movie-hiatus-coronavirus-1202893688/|archive-date=April 1, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n*''[[Vengeance (upcoming film)|Vengeance]]''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/secret-blumhouse-thriller-vengeance-suspends-production-coronavirus-concerns-1284712|title=Secret Blumhouse Thriller 'Vengeance' Suspends Production Over Coronavirus Concerns (Exclusive)|website=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|access-date=2020-03-14}}</ref>\n}}\n\n====Delayed====<!-- Films that were NOT in production but were due to be -->\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*''Bros''<ref name=\"UniversalProductionSuspensions\" />\n*''[[Wizarding World#Untitled third Fan